---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Cebu Builder's Circle">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900 to-slate-800 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-72 h-72 bg-amber-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-amber-500/3 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 py-20 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-full text-amber-400 text-sm font-medium mb-12 backdrop-blur-sm">
          🚀 Welcome to Cebu's Builder Circle
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="font-display text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-bold text-white mb-8 leading-[0.9] tracking-tight">
          What You Need to Know<br>
          <span class="text-amber-400 italic">Before You Join</span>
        </h1>
        
        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 font-light leading-relaxed">
            The Builder Circle is a focused, action-first space for people in Cebu who want to build and launch their own products, tools, or side projects.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 font-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
            It's not a community for passive inspiration — it's a circle of people who <strong class="text-slate-300">show up, build, and ship.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
            We help each other launch faster, learn quicker, and stay accountable — not by checking in constantly, but by staying committed to progress.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <p class="text-xl text-amber-400 font-semibold mb-4">This is not about startup hype or freelancing hustle.</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 font-light">This is about <strong class="text-white">independence through building — and weaving that into your lifestyle.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who This Is For Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-full text-amber-600 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
            🌎 Who This Is For
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">You're welcome here if you:</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm group hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-3"></div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Are working a job or freelancing, but want to build your own thing</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm group hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-3"></div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Have an idea, side project, or product you're ready to start (or restart)</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm group hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-3"></div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Want accountability and support to actually ship</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm group hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-3"></div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Believe in learning by doing, not just consuming</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm group hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-amber-500 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-3"></div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Are committed to helping others grow too</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl">
          <p class="text-lg text-amber-800 font-medium mb-2">Important:</p>
          <p class="text-amber-700 leading-relaxed">Skill level doesn't matter. <strong class="text-amber-800">Commitment does.</strong> We welcome builders using code, no-code, automation tools, AI — whatever helps you create and ship faster.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Builder's Pact Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-full text-amber-400 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
            ✅ What We Expect From You
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">The Builder's Pact</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 font-light">To stay aligned and high-signal, we ask everyone in the circle to agree to the following:</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-3xl p-12 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div class="space-y-12">
            <!-- You're building something -->
            <div class="border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">You're building something.</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">A landing page, tool, SaaS, newsletter, automation, product, or service.</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400 font-light italic">Doesn't need to be big or fancy. Just yours.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- You commit to progress -->
            <div class="border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">You commit to progress.</h3>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-lg">
                <p>• Show up in your own way: post updates, ask for help, or launch quietly</p>
                <p>• You're accountable to your build — not to appearances</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- You support others -->
            <div class="border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">You support others.</h3>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-lg">
                <p>• Give feedback, ideas, or encouragement</p>
                <p>• Celebrate small wins</p>
                <p>• Push others forward</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- You believe in momentum -->
            <div class="border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">You believe in momentum over perfection.</h3>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-lg">
                <p>• Launch fast. Learn faster.</p>
                <p>• Keep moving.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-600/50">
            <p class="text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
              There's no need to attend every gathering or post every week. But disappearing without progress? That's what we avoid. We stay light on meetings, heavy on momentum.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Meeting & Connection Culture Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-full text-slate-600 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
            👋 Meeting & Connection Culture
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">We believe in friendship-first.</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 font-light">You should be able to message or meet up with anyone here — casually, not formally.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              As we grow older, life tends to get scheduled, distant, and rigid. This circle is a return to <em class="text-slate-900 font-medium">organic connection</em>. Whether it's a spontaneous coffee catch-up or co-working jam, this is your builder crew.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              There will be occasional mandatory moments (like launch showcases or key meetups), but most interactions are built to feel natural, not burdensome.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="p-6 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800">This is a space for</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-green-700 leading-relaxed">Aligned people to stay connected through what they're building</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-6 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="text-2xl">❌</span>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-800">This isn't a place for</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-red-700 leading-relaxed">"Calendar guilt" or forced interactions</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tools & Platform Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-full text-slate-600 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
            🌐 Tools and Platform
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">We'll start with a Telegram group and Notion hub.</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-3xl">💬</span>
            </div>
                         <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Telegram</h3>
             <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Fast discussions, updates, casual meetups</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-3xl">📋</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Notion</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Project board, member profiles, resources, Builder's Hall of Fame</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl">
          <p class="text-amber-800 leading-relaxed">
            We may move to Discord or Circle once we grow. We'll evolve based on needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 rounded-full text-amber-600 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
            🎯 What to Expect Inside
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Regular activities that keep you shipping</h2>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Builder Toolkit & Resources -->
        <div class="mb-16 p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-3xl border border-blue-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-3xl">🧰</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Builder Toolkit & Resources</h3>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            A shared Notion vault where builders can find or contribute:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="space-y-3 text-slate-700">
              <p>• Landing page templates</p>
              <p>• Launch & feedback checklist</p>
              <p>• Automation & AI starter workflows</p>
              <p>• Product idea validation worksheet</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-slate-700">
              <p>• Pricing playbooks</p>
              <p>• Build-with-me replays or co-build replays</p>
              <p>• Curated tools for shipping fast (e.g. Framer, Carrd, Tally, n8n, Notion)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl">
            <p class="text-blue-800 font-medium">This helps new and veteran builders alike move faster — and not reinvent the wheel.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What Counts as Progress -->
        <div class="mb-16 p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-3xl border border-green-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-3xl">🧮</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">What Counts as Progress</h3>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Progress isn't always loud or polished. Here's what we recognize and celebrate:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-600 text-xl">✅</span>
                <p class="text-slate-700">You shipped something — anything, even a landing page</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-600 text-xl">✅</span>
                <p class="text-slate-700">You made updates to a previous project and relaunched</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-600 text-xl">✅</span>
                <p class="text-slate-700">You helped someone else build or get unstuck</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-600 text-xl">✅</span>
                <p class="text-slate-700">You shared honest struggles or asked for support</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-600 text-xl">✅</span>
                <p class="text-slate-700">You learned something that changes how you'll build</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl">
            <p class="text-green-800 text-lg font-medium mb-2">Progress isn't just about output — it's about <strong>momentum</strong>.</p>
            <p class="text-green-700">We don't pressure anyone to be perfect. We honor movement over maintenance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Weekly Build Prompts -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">⚡</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Weekly Build Prompts</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
              <p>• Simple challenge or question to spark momentum ("What can you launch in 3 hours?")</p>
              <p>• Share updates every Monday or Friday</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Monthly Demo Day -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">🎯</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Monthly Demo Day</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
              <p>• Share what you shipped (live or async)</p>
              <p>• Celebrate progress regardless of results</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Themed Builder Circles -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">🔄</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Themed Builder Circles <span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500">(bi-weekly or monthly)</span></h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Deep dives or open jam sessions (topics like: "Productized Services", "First Dollar Stories", "Automation Deep Dive", etc.)</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Peer Feedback Rounds -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">💬</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Peer Feedback Rounds</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Rotate feedback cycles: give & get insights from 1–2 members on your latest launch, roadmap, or stuck point</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Pop-up Sprints -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">🏃‍♂️</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Pop-up Sprints</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Weekend or week-long micro-hackathons focused on building & shipping one thing with optional co-building</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Builder Wall -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">🏆</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Builder Wall in Notion</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Profiles + public changelog per member so you can track your journey and others' too</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Collaboration Sparks -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-2xl">🤝</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Collaboration Sparks</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Optional "Help Board" where people post ideas or areas where they're open to team up (build/design/marketing/etc.)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl text-center">
          <p class="text-xl text-white font-light">This isn't about keeping busy. It's about building better — together.</p>
        </div>
        
                 <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
           <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
             <span class="text-2xl">🧭</span>
             <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Time Commitment</h3>
           </div>
           <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
             This isn't about being online or in-person all the time. We recommend carving <strong class="text-slate-900">1–2 hours/week</strong> to push something forward.
           </p>
           <p class="text-slate-600 font-light">
             You decide how you show up — what matters is that you <em>build</em>.
           </p>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Culture Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 rounded-full text-slate-600 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
            🌱 Culture, Support & Conduct
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">This is a trust-first, action-forward space</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 font-light">We take inspiration from <em>Everything is F*cked</em> by Mark Manson — recognizing that meaning comes from commitment, and real connection often stems from shared struggle.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-12 p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We're not here to create fake positivity or sugarcoat the hard parts of building. We support each other by:
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Acknowledging the mess.</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">Progress isn't always pretty — celebrate launches <em>and</em> lessons.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Choosing what matters.</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">We don't chase validation or followers. We commit to building what we believe in.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Showing real care.</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">When someone ships, we celebrate. When someone's stuck, we check in. No one builds alone.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl">
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              We honor the pain, doubt, and uncertainty that comes with building — not by solving it for each other, but by <strong class="text-white">staying in the arena</strong> together.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="p-6 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
